('7BMEqR9P', 'SandBox', 'std_companion_strings_xml', 'Good. I would merely ask from you an advance of {NPCPAYMENT}{GOLD_ICON}, to settle all affairs, and I shall join you.'),
('7bX48G5w', 'SandBox', 'std_wanderer_strings_xml', 'I was raised in a well-known clan, but my father died and my stepfather cast me out. It is a common enough story among our people. You may find many of us wandering the roads, our swords our only inheritance.'),
('7caHipXX', 'SandBox', 'std_wanderer_strings_xml', 'So I left. And a short while later the emperor sent a third detachment, bigger than the others, and that was the end of the Kingdom of Truth. My old comrades - I see them sometimes from time to time, some in a lord''s retinue, others in a cage with R for ''robber'' branded on their forehead.'),
