('7jBroUUQ', 'SandBox', 'std_StoryMode', 'Your family had little land of their own, so they earned their living from the woods, hunting and trapping. They taught you from an early age that skills like finding game trails and killing an animal with one shot could make the difference between eating and starvation.'),
