('7poObaCF', 'SandBox', 'std_world_lore_strings_xml', 'Yes, they needed a strong king, like a herd of cattle on a mountain trail needs a herdsman who knows the trail. Herds in the mountains, you see... Sometimes the stubborn old bulls, set in their ways, wander off the trail and lead the others toward a precipice.'),
('7pQ3y21E', 'SandBox', 'std_comment_strings_xml', 'Thank you again for all your help.'),
