('7qPda0SA', 'SandBox', 'std_SandBox', 'One of my relatives fell victim to his temper during a quarrel and killed a man from {TARGET_VILLAGE}. We have offered to pay blood money but the family of the deceased have stubbornly refused it. As it turns out, the deceased is kin to {TARGET_NOTABLE}, an elder of this region and now the men of {TARGET_VILLAGE} have sworn to kill my relative.'),
