('AWW0T6xR', 'Native', 'std_module_strings_xml', 'A pawn may be moved orthogonally, one tile at a time.{newline}A pawn can not be moved back to the tile that it came from in the previous turn.{newline}If a player is unable to move, that player may remove one of the opponent''s pawns and still make a move.'),
('aWWzrwAw', 'SandBox', 'std_TaleWorlds_CampaignSystem', 'The cost of revoking a fief from a clan is doubled\nClans gain 0.2 influence for each fief they own'),
