('aYozMy3Z', 'SandBox', 'std_StoryMode', 'We lost because the Vlandians broke their oaths, and fought us when they should have fought with us. I was given command of the cataphracts, and we easily crushed their crossbowmen. Their knights gave us more trouble. Meanwhile, the Sturgian infantry came down and attacked our main force. That’s where my father fell. '),
