('h4Pt3aX9', 'Native', 'std_multiplayer_strings_xml', 'Vlandian sergeants are commoners who found they have a knack for bloodletting. Often they''ve served time in a mercenary company, or drift from lord to lord. They''re famous throughout Calradia for their tenacity and professionalism. They are the anvil part of a Vlandian force''s ''Hammer and Anvil,'' the hammer of course being the knights.'),
