('J5sGlXzh', 'SandBox', 'std_wanderer_strings_xml', 'I was born with a birthmark on my shoulder in the shape of an eye. Whenever I passed my neighbors in the street, they made the sign of the Protector at me. They began to blame me for the sickness of children or livestock. '),
