('jaLrENzo', 'SandBox', 'std_wanderer_strings_xml', 'I need to buy a ship, and hire men to row it. But I do not wish to sell our land to outfit a risky voyage, to risk depriving my father and mother of their comforts in old age, and my brothers of their hopes for a good marriage.'),
