('sfFLudTM', 'SandBox', 'std_wanderer_strings_xml', 'One time they came at midnight - they had a man who plotted against the Emperor, they said, and they needed a confession, and wished me to use my art to elicit that confession. If I refused, they said, they would disclose our relationship to my patients - I would be ruined. I went with them, to my shame, and what I was asked to do to that man''s body -- I shall not repeat it.'),
