('XEuhxpCX', 'SandBox', 'std_StoryMode', 'Now, the Empire uses tricks and traps in war. No Battanian fears to meet an imperial soldier, man-to-man, but we thought it would be a good laugh to use their tricks against them. So we laid an ambush, on both sides of a wooded pass, and wouldn’t you know? They marched right into it.'),
